column5: Like to wish everybody a Happy New Year.Hope you all have a great 2017.
You also prov. Love to make it up to cedar this year and musky fish a day with you.
You too!!! I always like to hear insight from someone who is on the water daily.
only 6 months to go tank.lol. got a lot of ice fishing to do.but am looking forward to spring.
Happy New Years to Everyone. I hope everyone has a safe and fish filled year
Wishing a great and safe new year to everyone! And having to replace a reel or two due to a worn-out drag!! Bill
